---
Version information display

Usage: openssl version [OPTIONS]

Options:
  -a, --all             Print all version information (equivalent to enabling all flags)
  -v, --version         Print the OpenSSL version string
  -b, --build-date      Print the build date
  -p, --platform        Print the platform identifier
  -d, --config-dir      Print the OPENSSLDIR (configuration directory)
  -m, --modules-dir     Print the MODULESDIR (modules directory)
  -f, --compiler-flags  Print the compiler flags used during build
  -o, --options         Print the build options
  -r, --seed            Print the random seed source info
  -c, --cpu-settings    Print the CPU settings
  -h, --help            Print help
